The paper discusses optimization techniques for the Greedy Equivalence Search algorithm, which is commonly used in causal inference and machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The paper also discusses the use of supercomputers, which could fall under cs.SI (Systems and Control) or cs.IT (Information Theory).
